# /image

Transmits an image.

## `fen`

A FEN string.

## `flip`

The orientation of the board as per these options.

- `w` for White's perspective.
- `b` for Black's perspective.

---

#### Example

```js
ws.send('/image "{\\"fen\\":\\"r1bqkbnr/pppppppp/2n5/8/3PP3/8/PPP2PPP/RNBQKBNR b KQkq d3\\", \\"flip\\":\\"b\\"}"');
```
